News.headline: DON'T FORGET: Emirates FA Cup Second Round Draw
News.page_title: DON'T FORGET: Emirates FA Cup Second Round Draw
News.URL_keywords: DON'T FORGET: Emirates FA Cup Second Round Draw
News.short_description: The Emirates FA Cup second round draw will be live on Monday 7th November from 7pm.
News.description:
After the Daggers' 0-0 draw with FC Halifax Town the Daggers will have to over come a replay in order to confirm their place in the Emirates FA Cup second round draw.
  
The Daggers or FC Halifax Town will be ball number 3 in the first round draw taking place tonight at approximately 7:10pm, which you can watch live on BT Sport 1 and BBC 2.

To find out more about the draw and see the other teams numbers click here.
